VERSION HISTORY

= v0.2.X 

  * Adds a 'bocuse' hash, containing relevant information about the current
    node and project. Currently only :node_name will be defined. 
  ! Remove all Ruby warnings. 
  * Also allows bocuse hash in the context of a template. 
  ! 'test' can now be a recipe name used in #cook.

= v0.1.2

  * Allows 'method' and other standard Ruby methods as keys in pseudo-hashes. 

= v0.1.1

  * Syntax sugar for 'cook foo, cfg.foo do ... end'. Append the block to cook
    directly. 

= v0.1.0

  * Nodes/Templates
  * Helper methods
  * Rocks.